VINCULOS.OUTRAS-INFORMACOES:
[EN] Brief description of the topics of the PhD thesis:

(a) Earth surface geophysical parameters estimation, focusing on land and sea surface temperatures, from infrared data, acquired by remote sensors onboard geostationary and polar orbit satellites (AVHRR, SEVIRI), using regression architectures based on Support Vector Machines (SVM);

(b) Supervised classification of optical high spatial resolution remotely sensed imagery using ensemble classifiers based on SVMs and texture information to represent spatial information.
